queries.sql: SELECT `ml`.*, `sr`.`recipient_id` as `recipient_code`, `sr`.`first_name`, `sr`.`last_name`, `sr`.`middle_name`, `sr`.`campus` as `recipient_campus`, `ml`.`campus` as `campus`, `u1`.`username` as `disbursing_officer`, `u2`.`username` as `scholarship_coordinator` FROM `manual_liquidations` `ml` LEFT JOIN `scholarship_recipients` `sr` ON `ml`.`recipient_id` = `sr`.`id` LEFT JOIN `users` `u1` ON `ml`.`disbursing_officer_id` = `u1`.`id` LEFT JOIN `users` `u2` ON `ml`.`scholarship_coordinator_id` = `u2`.`id` WHERE `ml`.`status` != 'hidden' AND `ml`.`campus` = 'Main Campus'
